						<div class="postbody">OK, Ironsword doesn't have the problem because the loop that clears APU registers <em>reads</em> the register first since it uses the STA $4000,x addressing mode. So that reads $4015 after the frame IRQ flag has been set. This game should work regardless of the VBL flag at power. Same issue for Cobra Triangle (I checked init code too).
<br />
<br /><div class="quotetitle">hap wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Are you modifying it during rendering?</div>hmmmmm... *shameful yes*<br />none of your test roms cover it <img src="./images/smilies/icon_wink.gif" alt=";)" title="Wink" /></div>
